  "notes": [
    "All endpoints require Bearer token authentication",
    "Replace 'YOUR_API_TOKEN' with your actual Odoo API token",
    "For GET requests, use query parameters (e.g., ?limit=50&offset=0)",
    "For POST requests, send JSON data in the request body",
    "Country can be specified by name (e.g., 'United States') or code (e.g., 'US')",
    "State/Province requires country_id to be set first",
    "Empty string fields will be returned as empty strings, not null",
    "The API uses pagination with limit and offset parameters"
